title: VonZipper: Ladies Sunglasses 2013
description:
VonZipper's latest fashion film will surely make you miss summer. Set to "Let It Roll" by LA-based garage rock trio Wake Up Lucid, the sun-dappled mini-movie features the sunglass designer's newest styles. You can pick up Wake Up Lucid's new 7-inch below... or even better, download the track below after you watch the VonZipper clip for free. Shop the new VonZipper women's sunglasses right here:

http://vonzipper.com/ladies

WAKE UP LUCID
"Let It Roll"

The featured song "Let It Roll" is part of a new 7-inch record the band put out this month on Near Mess Records
